title: FRIDAY 4/23- JETS NOT TIPPING THEIR PICK
itunes:title: FRIDAY 4/23- JETS NOT TIPPING THEIR PICK
description:
The Jets hold the 2nd pick in the draft, but GM Joe Douglas (0:06) says he doesn't want to give away who they plan to pick, but head coach Robert Saleh (0:25) not worried if it's a QB. The Cardinals already have their franchise QB, so head coach Kliff Kingsbury (1:06) hoping there's a run on QBs early in the draft. Raiders GM Mike Mayock (1:44) going into the draft with an open mind, while Broncos GM George Paton (2:26) decides what to do at the QB position. Plus, Myles Garrett (2:44) excited about the Browns defense
